<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank you for your feedback</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2d3748;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .feedback-summary {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .feedback-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
        }
        
        .feedback-type {
            background: #4299e1;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .feedback-type.positive { background: #48bb78; }
        .feedback-type.negative { background: #f56565; }
        .feedback-type.suggestion { background: #ed8936; }
        .feedback-type.bug { background: #e53e3e; }
        .feedback-type.feature_request { background: #9f7aea; }
        
        .rating {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .stars {
            color: #f6ad55;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .feedback-content {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4299e1;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #4a5568;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .details-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #718096;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #2d3748;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .tracking-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef5e7 0%, #fed7aa 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        
        .tracking-id {
            font-family: 'SF Mono', Monaco, 'Cascadia Code', 'Roboto Mono', Consolas, 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #c05621;
            background: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 12px 0;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .message-box {
            background: #e6fffa;
            border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .message-box h4 {
            color: #234e52;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .message-box p {
            color: #285e61;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #4299e1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #4a5568;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .details-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 16px;
            }
            
            .feedback-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Thank You! üôè</h1>
            <p>Your feedback has been received and is greatly appreciated</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{submitterName}},
            </div>
            
            <p>Thank you for sharing your thoughts about <strong>{{featureName}}</strong> in {{applicationName}}. Your feedback helps us create better experiences for everyone.</p>
            
            <div class="feedback-summary">
                <div class="feedback-header">
                    <span class="feedback-type {{feedbackType}}">{{uppercase feedbackType}}</span>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <span class="stars">{{ratingStars}}</span>
                        <span>{{rating}}/5</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feedback-content">
                    "{{feedbackContent}}"
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <div class="detail-label">Application</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{applicationName}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <div class="detail-label">Feature</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{featureName}}</div>
                </div>
                {{#if environment}}
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <div class="detail-label">Environment</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{uppercase environment}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <div class="detail-label">Submitted</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate submissionDate}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if trackingId}}
            <div class="tracking-section">
                <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #c05621;">üìã Your Reference ID</h3>
                <div class="tracking-id">{{trackingId}}</div>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: #744210; font-size: 14px;">Save this for future reference</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if confirmationMessage}}
            <div class="message-box">
                <h4>üí¨ Message from our team</h4>
                <p>{{confirmationMessage}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>Our team will review your feedback and take appropriate action. {{#ifEquals feedbackType 'bug'}}We'll investigate the issue and work on a fix.{{else}}We'll consider your input for future improvements.{{/ifEquals}}</p>
            
            {{#if supportEmail}}
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The {{companyName}} Team</strong></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{formatDate submissionDate}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            {{#if supportEmail}}
            <p>Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 